freesmartphone.org Framework DBus Interface Specification

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Fields

Description

This interface provides access to field types in domains.

Namespace

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Fields

Methods

  • AddField
  • DeleteField
  • GetType
  • ListFields
  • ListFieldsWithType

Signals

None

Errors

None

Methods

Description: Add new field to the list.

Parameters

s: name

The field's name.

s: type

The field's type.

DeleteField ( s )

Description: Delete field from list.

Parameters

s: name

The field's name.

GetType ( s ) → s

Description: Get type of specified field.

Parameters

s: name

The field's name.

Returns

s: type

The field's type.

ListFields ( ) → a{ss}

Description: List all specified fields and their types.

Returns

a{ss}: fields

A dictionary with field names and types.

ListFieldsWithType ( s ) → as

Description: List all fields with specified type.

Parameters

s: type

Field type.

Returns

as: fields

A list with field names.
